text: Camilla Joy Cynthia Power (born 13 November 1976) is an Irish-born English actress. She is best known for portraying the roles of Jessica McAllister in the ITV soap opera Emmerdale (1993–1995), and Lorna Dickey in the BBC school- based drama series Waterloo Road (2006–2007). ==Personal life== Power was born in Cork, Ireland, but grew up in Wimbledon and Putney, England. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:English television actors Category:English movie actors Category:Actors from Cork (city)
title: Camilla Power
